  "detailed_description": "Kill To Live is a single player military first person shooter. Your task is simple - to get to the exit, killing as many enemy soldiers as possible along the way. Your health decreases with every second and extermination of enemies is the most effective way to restore it. At your service is an arsenal of modern weapons and five spacious arenas. Show your accuracy!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854890/extras/1e5d5b6eb56e8ff70af950f2dd451482.avif?t=1681550395\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Continuous shooting<br></li><li> Five levels<br></li><li> Five types of weapons<br></li><li> Realistic graphics<br></li><li> Dynamic soundtrack</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854890/extras/ee0625fea453058e240180b416ffeb48.avif?t=1681550395\" width=600 height=200 /></span>",
